enumeratedData.name: LinkStatus
enumeratedData.semantics: kLinkUnknown = 0, // The link state could not be determined (e.g. lost connection to board) kLinkDown = 1, // Link is down kLinkUp = 2, // Link is up kLinkNegotiate = 3, // Link is currently performing auto-negotiation kLinkError = 4 // Link is in error state (e.g. auto-negotiation failed)

arrayData.name: CANMessageData
arrayData.semantics: Bytes carried in a CAN frame. Note that the actual number of bytes is carried in a distinct member field of the CANFrame.

arrayData.name: EthernetPacketData
arrayData.semantics: Bytes carried in a Ethernet Packet. The data is variable-sized and carries the actual number of bytes used.

arrayData.name: FlexRayPayloadData
arrayData.semantics: Bytes carried in a FlexRay Frame. The data is variable-sized and carries the actual number of bytes used.

fixedRecordData.name: BusEvent
fixedRecordData.semantics: Base class for all bus events, inclulding error and status events

fixedRecordData.name: BusMessage
fixedRecordData.semantics: Base class for all other bus messages

field.name: Data
field.semantics: Data bytes of the CAN Message (up to 64 bytes)

field.name: ErrorBitPosition
field.semantics: difference between EOF and SOF in ns

field.name: FrameLengthNS
field.semantics: difference between EOF and SOF in ns
